data.--unitone--min-half-leading#--unitone--m:
As explained above, the minimum line-height is 1.1. The minimum value is determined by the following formula.
line-height: calc(1 + 2 * var(--unitone--min-half-leading));
This value can be customized.

data.import-css#Import CSS:
To import CSS for unitone CSS, @use in your main SCSS file. In the case of HTML, you can also use <link /> to load CSS.
@use 'PATH/TO/node_modules/@inc2734/unitone-css/src/app';
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/node_modules/@inc2734/unitone-css/dist/app.css" />

data.import-javascript#Import JavaScript:
To import JavaScript for unitone CSS, @import in your main JavaScript file. In the case of HTML, you can also use <script /> to load JavaScript.
import '@inc2734/unitone-css/app';
<script src="/node_modules/@inc2734/unitone-css/dist/app.js"></script>

